extends layout

block content

  //- ─── PAGE HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.page-hero.section
    .container
      .page-hero-inner.page-hero-inner--centered
        span.section-eyebrow Our story
        h1.page-hero-title Built for African fashion.
          br
          | Built for you.
        p.page-hero-subtitle Hedge Wears was born from a simple frustration: local fashion designers were building incredible things, but had no direct way to reach the people who would love their work.

  //- ─── MISSION ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.mission.section.section--dark
    .container
      .mission-inner
        .mission-statement
          span.section-eyebrow Our mission
          blockquote.mission-quote
            | &ldquo;To connect fashion creators with fashion lovers &mdash; and make every purchase a step toward something more.&rdquo;
        .mission-body
          p We started Hedge Wears to give local fashion brands a platform that works as hard as they do. A place where sellers can list their products, manage their business, and get paid &mdash; all without the complexity of building their own store from scratch.
          p For shoppers, we wanted fashion discovery to feel exciting and rewarding. Not just buying clothes, but earning something back each time you do. That&rsquo;s where HedgeCoin came in &mdash; a loyalty system that turns your spending into savings.
          p Today, Hedge Wears connects thousands of shoppers with hundreds of brands, with new sellers and products added every day.

  //- ─── VALUES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.values.section
    .container
      .section-header
        span.section-eyebrow What we believe
        h2.section-title Our values

      .values-grid
        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            span.value-icon ◆
          h3.value-title Local first
          p.value-desc We champion African designers and fashion entrepreneurs. Hedge Wears is a platform built to amplify local talent, not displace it.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            span.value-icon ◈
          h3.value-title Transparency
          p.value-desc Pricing is clear. HedgeCoin is straightforward. No hidden fees, no confusing terms. What you see is what you get.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            span.value-icon ◉
          h3.value-title Rewarding loyalty
          p.value-desc Shopping here should benefit you every time. The HedgeCoin reward system exists to give back to the people who keep the platform alive: our customers.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            span.value-icon ○
          h3.value-title Simple by design
          p.value-desc Every feature we ship has to earn its place. If it doesn&rsquo;t make shopping or selling meaningfully easier, we cut it.

  //- ─── BUILT FOR AFRICA ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.africa.section.section--muted
    .container
      .africa-inner
        .africa-content
          span.section-eyebrow Where we&rsquo;re headed
          h2.africa-title Fashion without borders
          p Hedge Wears launched in Nigeria but was always designed to grow. Our multi-currency support means shoppers can view prices in their local currency, and our seller tools are built to support brands shipping across borders.
          p We believe Africa&rsquo;s fashion industry is one of the most vibrant in the world. Our goal is to build the infrastructure that lets it reach a global audience.
        .africa-stats
          .africa-stat-card
            span.africa-stat-num 10,000+
            span.africa-stat-label Products available
          .africa-stat-card
            span.africa-stat-num 500+
            span.africa-stat-label Active stores
          .africa-stat-card
            span.africa-stat-num 15+
            span.africa-stat-label Currencies supported
          .africa-stat-card
            span.africa-stat-num 50,000+
            span.africa-stat-label Customers

  //- ─── TEAM / PLACEHOLDER ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.team.section
    .container
      .section-header
        span.section-eyebrow The people
        h2.section-title Behind Hedge Wears
        p.section-subtitle We&rsquo;re a small team of designers, engineers, and fashion enthusiasts working to build something lasting.

      .team-grid
        .team-card.team-card--placeholder
          .team-avatar-placeholder
          .team-info
            span.team-name Founder &amp; CEO
            span.team-role Building the vision
        .team-card.team-card--placeholder
          .team-avatar-placeholder
          .team-info
            span.team-name Head of Product
            span.team-role Designing the experience
        .team-card.team-card--placeholder
          .team-avatar-placeholder
          .team-info
            span.team-name Lead Engineer
            span.team-role Shipping the platform
        .team-card.team-card--placeholder
          .team-avatar-placeholder
          .team-info
            span.team-name Growth &amp; Partnerships
            span.team-role Growing the community

      p.team-footer-note
        | Want to join the team?&nbsp;
        a.link(href='/careers') See open roles

  //- ─── CONTACT CTA ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.cta-banner.section
    .container
      .cta-banner-inner
        h2.cta-banner-title Got questions?
        p.cta-banner-subtitle We&rsquo;d love to hear from you &mdash; whether you&rsquo;re a shopper, a brand, or just curious.
        .cta-banner-actions
          a.btn.btn-white.btn-lg(href='/contact') Get in Touch
          a.btn.btn-outline-white.btn-lg(href='https://hedgewears.com/shop' target='_blank' rel='noopener') Visit the Store
